{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 261.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, whatever the green light is-- you know, whether our number comes up, whether the visas are finally gotten, we go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we go to New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The new life still obviously flowing out of the old life, yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are put up-- my uncle is the one with the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one who got out of Austria lives in New York-- a very elegant apartment on the West Side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are initially put in little, rented apartments in a hotel on the West Side called the Hotel Churchill.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "New York, at that point-- this is 1941, but before the United States has gotten into the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "New York-- Upper West Side of New York feels to me, as a child, like the way the movie feels when you see it today, full of refugees-- German, Polish, whatever-- sitting in cafeterias, smoking endless cigarettes, discussing you know, their situation.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's very war-influenced, that part of the city, because there's so many refugees who are at least temporarily staying there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we're staying in this little apartment, two rooms-- one for my parents, one for my sister and me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But cramped and tiny as that little place is compared to what I have known as a young child, there is definitely this feeling.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember, I think, asking my parents that repeatedly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're not going to have to move anymore?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because up to that point, it's always a feeling that I move, you move, you move, you move, you move, you-- there is no home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if they had given us one room, it would have felt great.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And did they try to construct their lives as Jews in New York?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How do they do that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
